reviewText: Internal Behaviors The MovieTHIS IS ONE "KOOL" & "HIP" MOVIE. IT HAS FIGHTING, ACTION, BLOOD, DANCING AND MARTIAL ARTS. AND IT HAS A GREAT MUSIC SOUND TRACK.
